{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636430/extras/Fish.gif?t=1737512967\" />Soggy Beans is a relaxing side-idler where fish visit you. Think bird watching, but with fish. Decorate, take pictures, complete photography quests, or just let your friends keep you company while you do other things.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636430/extras/Header_Spot.gif?t=1737512967\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636430/extras/Discover.gif?t=1737512967\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Find fish of all shapes and sizes.</strong> Fish come and go as they please, spot new ones as they visit and record each sighting in your journal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636430/extras/Header_Journal.gif?t=1737512967\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636430/extras/Journal.gif?t=1737512967\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Keep track of all the fish</strong> you see, update their profiles, and watch as your journal grows.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636430/extras/Header_Pics.gif?t=1737512967\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2636430/extras/Camera.gif?t=1737512967\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Capture photos 